    <tags>glanvu image viewer converter graphics photo</tags>
    <summary>Fast, keyboard-driven, cross-platform universal image viewer and converter</summary>
    <description>
Glanvu is a fast, GPU-accelerated image viewer and converter for Linux, macOS and Windows.
It loads instantly, navigates entire folders by keyboard, and includes a real batch-convert
pipeline (crop, rotate, resize, re-quality, rename). Supports JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, BMP and
TIFF via pure-Rust codecs — no system C libraries.

The `glanvu` command works both as a GUI viewer and a headless batch converter.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/glanvu/glanvu/releases/tag/v0.6.1</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
